        {
            "title": "荃錦公路3私家車相撞 一司機受傷送院",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"荃錦公路發生3車相撞意外。網圖\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/9a6acd1fce65dd4e63d251a307676348/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250403/_2025040301354670254.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">荃錦公路發生3車相撞意外。網圖</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>荃錦公路發生車禍。周三（2日）晚上11時許，一輛寶馬私家車沿荃錦公路往荃灣方向行駛，當駛至曹公潭戶外康樂中心對開一右彎時，寶馬懷疑失控越過對面行車線，迎頭與一輛本田私家車及一相撞，尾隨的Kia私家車收掣不及撞向本田車尾。\n\n</p>\n<p>寶馬男司機及女乘客一度被困車內，Kia巴基斯坦籍男司機見狀下，立即下車幫手救人。救援人員趕至現場，將傷者救出，清醒由救護車送往醫院治理。警方正調查意外原因。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4174198/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"安全氣袋彈出。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4b2f8a3c5fbcedba90560c062d5e864f/2025-04/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-04-03-00-34-29_001.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        安全氣袋彈出。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4174199/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"本田擋風玻璃損毀。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3bc27a54568ffc1f1db788d660df57f2/2025-04/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-04-03-00-34-29_002.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        本田擋風玻璃損毀。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4174200/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"Kia收掣不及撞向本田私家車。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/dd08fab69b062e694768fa34f5764be0/2025-04/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-04-03-00-34-33_003.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Kia收掣不及撞向本田私家車。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4174201/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"本田私家車車頭嚴重損毀。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/29635a524aece730ff048e455bac6d6b/2025-04/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-04-03-00-34-42_005.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        本田私家車車頭嚴重損毀。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4174202/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"寶馬由拖車拖走。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/905717c5fd2f41b732477984ad9386dd/2025-04/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-04-03-00-34-37_004.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        寶馬由拖車拖走。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>涉事的寶馬及本田私家車車頭嚴重損毀。受事件影響，來回行車線一度封閉。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
